data.title: 5 - Q3 Sci
data.meta_description: 5_Q3 SCI - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides an overview of a science module that discusses climate. It includes a description of the learning competencies, objectives, and development team for the module. The module will explain how factors such as latitude, altitude, distance from bodies of water, ocean currents, and topography affect the climate of different areas.
